high_descs: Turn around, then turn left at the window and walk to the counter with the coffee machine on it.
Pick up the mug from the coffee machine.
Turn to the stove to the left of the counter.
Place the mug in the microwave above the stove, warm it, then take it out.
Walk back to the coffee machine.
Place the mug in the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed mug in a coffee machine.

high_descs: Move forward then left, then head to the coffee maker
Pick up the mug on the  coffee maker
Turn to your left head toward the microwave above the stove
Open the microwave put in the mug then pick it up and close the microwave
Turn to your right move forward face the coffee maker
Put the mug on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the warm mug on the coffee maker

high_descs: Grab the coffee cup that is under on coffee pot
Carry the cup to the microwave
Put the coffee cup in the microwave
Take the coffee cup out of the microwave
Carry the cup back to the coffee pot
anns.task_desc: Heating up a cup of coffee
